==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ecballium
<hw>Ec*bal"li*um</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. Gr.
<?/. See <er>Ecbole</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of
cucurbitaceous plants consisting of the single species <xex>Ecballium
agreste</xex> (or <xex>Elaterium</xex>), the squirting cucumber. Its
fruit, when ripe, bursts and violently ejects its seeds, together with a
mucilaginous juice, from which elaterium, a powerful cathartic medicine,
is prepared.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

